md:
giải nghĩa từ "final" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan.

Final /ˈfaɪnəl/ (adjective)

* Meaning: happening or done at the end of something; last in a series of things
* Vietnamese: cuối cùng, sau cùng

Example sentence: The final exam is on Friday.

* Related words: last, ultimate, concluding, terminal

Final /ˈfaɪnəl/ (noun)

* Meaning: the last part or stage of something
* Vietnamese: phần cuối, giai đoạn cuối

Example sentence: The final of the tennis tournament was very exciting.

* Related words: conclusion, ending, termination, climax

Note: The word "final" can also be used as an adverb, meaning "in a final manner" or "at the end of something". For example: "The team played final in the championship game."
